      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Port_Norris%2C_New_Jersey"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "In the early 1990s, the Maurice River received National Scenic and Recreational River status, protecting 35.4 miles of pristine corridor.",
